AUTHOR     (R.M.Gaedke,K.S.Toth,I.R.Williams)
TITLE      Cross-Section Measurement for the Nucleon-Transfer
            Reactions 10B(19F,18F)11B and 10B(19F,18O)11C.
FACILITY   (VDGT,1USAORL)
DETECTOR   Low-level gas flow beta detector.
METHOD     (ACTIV)
           Measured thick target yields.
REL-REF    (R,,S.K.Allison+,J,RMP,25,779,1953)
           Stopping powers used to calculate cross sections were
           taken from Allison and Warshaw, Rev.Mod.Phys.25,779.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Estimate of absolute uncertainty, includes
            uncertainties due to counter efficiency, slope of
            yield curves, and stopping powers.
           Estimated thick target yield uncertainty 15%.
STATUS     (CPX) Data from CPX-file compiled in 1964/67 by
           F.K.McGowan et al.
HISTORY    (19990308A) Converted from data set P0144, BIB update.
           (20260121U) OS. Minor correction in subs.4,6, BIB
            updates
